summary: Disables the \"Unable to Fast Travel from this location\" Message, for anyone using methods to disable fast travel.
descriptionHtml:
Disables the \"Unable to Fast Travel from this location\" Message, for anyone using methods to disable fast travel.

It\'s recommended to use this mod with Fast Travel disabled, here are some useful links:

No Fast Travel by NullCascade (requires Script Dragon): http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2075

Or to disable fast travel without using mods open SkyrimPrefs.ini and add EnableFastTravel=0 to the [General] section


Install this mod by extracting DisableNoFastTravelMessage.esp to the data folder
author: Jjiinx
